<br />

<br />
You asked about flash players, well they dont make 10GB flash players, 1 or 2 GB is as big as I know about.  Creative Muvo is the way to go for flash players.  Good price good features good sound quality.  I have a Sandisk flash player and its great except 128kbs mp3's have cracks pops and skips that dont exist when played on my computer or in my car.  192kbs mp3's play fine on the flash player though, I would have thought it to be the other way around.<br />
